captions.text:
-Hi, we're the twins
from Brooklyn and Bailey.

-Today we're going to show you
a video of a really fun activity

It's called Foam
Days, which you'll
know why once you see the video.

They literally take
a huge soccer field

-Well, the firefighters
came and sprayed foam--

It's up to here, up to
your eyeballs with foam.

-You can bring all
your friends and family
and it's a really fun activity.

-It's a whole soccer
field of foam.

Anyways, this is our family's
experience with this Foam Days.

-Can you see all the
foam they're spraying?

And a gajillion people
come, you can see.

And let their kids run
around through the foam.

And down there they have all
these bouncy houses and slides.

And all this other
stuff, and every year it

We're going to go and
play in the foam today.

The kids love this because
they just get all sudsy.

-We are all dressed
and ready to go,
so let's see how this works.

Run and do a dive
or something cool.

You're a little bit
too clean, child.
I don't know where she went.

I seriously don't
know where she went.

The girls are out
there somewhere
sud surfing in all that foam.

I don't even know
where they are anymore.

OK, I figured out
where they are.

In the midst of all that
craziness right there.
That is an awesome swim cap.

-Wasn't that funny when
we hugged our Grandpa?

How many of you guys have
hugged your grandparents

or your parents when
you're all wet and dirty?

We want to know what kind of
fun things your city does.

And then he's like,
I like your sleeves.
